For some, work is winding down, and people are headed out the door early. It's overcast outside, and it would seem some detectives are eager to turn in before the rain complicates traffic. Ernest has taken the rest of the day off- opting to walk so as to not disrupt his housemate's work itinerary- and it would seem like he managed to have a brief conversation with his brother on the phone before he left. Well, time to settle down. The client will be here any minute now. @luminaries
